'''返嬰癖'''（{{lang-en|Paraphilic infantilism}}或{{lang|en|autonepiophilia}}<ref>{{cite book|ref=harv|last=Corsini|first=Raymond J.|title=The Dictionary of Psychology|year=2002|publisher=Psychology Press|isbn=978-1-58391-328-4|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=0uxnglHzYaoC&pg=PA374|access-date=2017-02-14|archive-date=2017-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170818035836/https://books.google.com/books?id=0uxnglHzYaoC&pg=PA374|dead-url=no}}</ref>）又稱成年嬰兒綜合症（{{lang-en|adult baby syndrome}}<ref name = Russell>{{cite book |ref = harv | last = Russell | first = J | year = 2008 | title = Exploring Psychology for AS Level AQA 'A'| isbn = 1-85008-258-8 | publisher = Folens Limited | pages =[https://books.google.com/books?id=4ereiHom3d8C&pg=PA200#v=onepage&q&f=false 200]}}</ref>）是一種涉及以角色扮演的方式成為類似嬰兒的型態的性慾倒錯或心態<ref name = Hickey>{{cite book|ref=harv|last=Hickey|first=Eric W.|title=Sex Crimes and Paraphilia | publisher= [[Pearson_Education|Pearson Education]] |year=2006|isbn=978-0-13-170350-6 | pages =355}}</ref><ref name = Speaker>{{citation | last = Speaker | first = TJ | title = Psychosexual Infantilism in Adults: The Eroticization of Regression | publisher = Columbia Pacific University | pages = 93 | location = Sausalito, CA }}</ref>。行為可能包括用使用[[嬰兒奶瓶|奶瓶]]或[[尿布|尿布]]。<ref name = Russell/>{{sfn|Money|1986|p=[https://books.google.com/books?id=OpkY2Fqwx_UC&pg=PA70 70]}}。這種經驗可以是充滿溫柔與呵護的<ref name = Brame>{{cite book | last = Brame | first = GG |author2=Brame WD |author3=Jacobs J | title = Different Loving: An Exploration of the World of Sexual Dominance and Submission | publisher = [[Random_House|Random House of Canada]] | year = 1996 | pages = [https://books.google.com/books?id=yA-P9ucEbYgC&pg=PA137#v=onepage&q&f=false 137–40] | isbn = 0-679-76956-0}}</ref>，（只有參與扮演嬰幼兒的成年人稱為成年嬰兒<ref name="pate" />）或是[[受虐癖|受虐待]]、強迫、懲罰、羞辱的<ref name = Brame/> 。與[[戀尿布|戀尿布]]不同的是，戀尿布不見得涉及模仿嬰兒的行為<ref name="Kise">{{Cite journal | last1 = Kise | first1 = K. | last2 = Nguyen | first2 = M. | title = Adult Baby Syndrome and Gender Identity Disorder | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_archives-of-sexual-behavior_2011-10_40_5/page/857 | doi = 10.1007/s10508-011-9783-8 | journal = [[Archives_of_Sexual_Behavior|Archives of Sexual Behavior]]| year = 2011 | pmid =  | pmc = | volume = 40| issue = 5| pages = 857–859 }}</ref> 。而同時有這兩種情況的人稱為成年嬰兒/尿布愛好者（AB/DL）<ref>{{cite news | last = Watson | first = J | date = 2005-06-09 | url = http://www.phoenixnewtimes.com/2005-06-09/news/baby-man/ | title = Baby Man | work = [[Phoenix_New_Times|Phoenix New Times]] | accessdate = 2011-02-28 | archive-date = 2011-04-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110430181648/http://www.phoenixnewtimes.com/2005-06-09/news/baby-man/ | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="taormino">{{cite news | last = Taormino | first = T | url = http://www.villagevoice.com/2002-08-13/columns/still-in-diapers/ | title = Still in Diapers | accessdate = 2007-05-08 | work = [[The_Village_Voice|The Village Voice]] | date = 2002-08-13 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080920143752/http://www.villagevoice.com/2002-08-13/columns/still-in-diapers/ | archivedate = 2008-09-20 }}</ref>，當穿尿布時，返嬰癖會在尿布中[[排尿|排尿]]或[[排便|排便]]。<ref name = Speaker/>

雖然有一些片段的論述，但目前尚未有關於這個主題的正式研究、也沒有公認的病理原因。它與受虐狂及其他類型的性慾倒錯經常被連結，也常常會與戀童癖混淆，不過返嬰癖和戀童癖是不一樣的，返嬰癖不會將兒童做為性伴侶<ref name = Arndt>{{cite book|ref=harv|last=Arndt|first=William B.|title=Gender Disorders and Paraphilias|publisher=International Universities Press|year=1991|isbn=978-0-8236-2150-7 | pages = 394}}</ref><ref name = Tiefenwerth>{{cite book|ref=harv|last=Tiefenwerth|first=Thomas J.|title= Criminal Sexuality and Psychopathology: Pornography as a Contributory Risk Factor in the Psycho-Social Development of Violent Sex Offenders | publisher=[[ProQuest|ProQuest]] |year=2007|isbn=978-0-549-14928-6 | pages = 111 }}</ref>。世界各地上已經成立了許多旨在促進返嬰癖與能滿足返嬰癖者的組織。

== 特徵和行為 ==
一位在戀嬰癖社群內人士陳述，這個圈子主要由兩類人組成：其一是成年嬰兒（由成人扮演成嬰兒），其二是sissy babies<!--請求除了娘娘腔嬰兒以外的翻譯-->（傾向穿著女性服飾、並使用女性代詞）。除此之外還有不扮演成嬰兒的[[戀尿布|戀尿布]]者，或是用尿布用於[[支配與臣服|支配與臣服]]關係手段之一的支配者。雖然區分出了幾個類別，但不同類別的人所從事的行為是高度重疊的<ref name="taormino"/> ，而為了喚起性刺激而扮演成嬰兒或小孩的成年人更被認為是返嬰癖的象徵標記{{sfn|Money|1986|p=[https://books.google.com/books?id=OpkY2Fqwx_UC&pg=PA70 70]}}<ref name = holmes/>。這些行為可能包括使用成人尺寸的尿布、嬰兒服飾、玩具或家具（例如嬰兒床）以求在環境上營造真實感<ref>{{cite book | last = Baumeister | first = RF | year = 1989 | title = Masochism and Self | publisher = Lawrence Erlbaum Associates | pages = 159 | isbn = 0-8058-0486-2}}</ref><ref name = Cantor/> ，也可能在地上如嬰兒般爬行、或是使用尿布來排泄<ref name = Cantor/><ref name =Speaker/><ref name = holmes/><ref name = Cantor/>，如果有合作夥伴配合，則成年嬰兒可以進行親子角色扮演，扮演內容包括使用奶瓶、洗澡、穿尿布、在尿布裏排泄及換尿布<ref name = Cantor/>{{sfn|Money|1986|p=[https://books.google.com/books?id=OpkY2Fqwx_UC&pg=PA70 70]}}<ref name = holmes/>、或是哺乳<ref name = holmes>{{cite book|ref=harv|last1=Holmes|first1=Ronald M.|last2=Holmes|first2=Stephen T.|title=Sex Crimes: Patterns and Behavior | publisher = [[SAGE_Publications|SAGE Publications]] | year = 2008 | isbn = 1-4129-5298-0 | pages = [https://books.google.com/books?id=_zqOsZSZxYQC&pg=PA81#v=onepage&q&f=false 81]}}</ref> {{sfn|Money|1986|p=[https://books.google.com/books?id=OpkY2Fqwx_UC&pg=PA70 70]}}。在某些情境下，可能會有因為嬰兒弄溼或弄髒尿布而受到責罵、打屁股或懲罰的狀況{{sfn|Money|1986|p=[https://books.google.com/books?id=OpkY2Fqwx_UC&pg=PA70 70]}}。其它的情境可能僅有溫柔的培育或呵護，以及「拋開各種成人肩負的責任」<ref name = Ditmore/>。此外、有一些情境可能會涉及手淫和射精<ref name = Cantor/><ref name = Ditmore>{{cite book | last = Ditmore | first = MH | title = Encyclopedia of prostitution and sex work, Volume 1 | isbn = 0-313-32968-0 | publisher = [[Greenwood_Publishing_Group|Greenwood Publishing Group]] | year = 2006 | pages = [https://books.google.com/books?id=fcYq72qYRTcC&pg=PA238#v=onepage&q&f=false 238] }}</ref>，而其它的情況則是沒有性的，因為嬰兒是無性的{{sfn|Stekel|1952|pp=143–144}}。返嬰癖帶有性愉悅的體驗可以取代他們在性交中達到性高潮的需要。{{sfn|Money|1986|p=[https://books.google.com/books?id=OpkY2Fqwx_UC&pg=PA70 70]}}

在一項針對了包含93%的男性（不含跨性別者）的AB/DL參與者的研究中，58%的男性和34%的女性是異性戀，男性對AB/DL初次感興趣的平均年齡是11歲，而實際嘗試的平均年齡是13歲，女性則分別為12歲及16歲。最常見的活動是穿尿布、[[尿床|尿床]]、使用嬰兒用品。87%的男性和91%的女性表示他們的AB/DL活動沒有引起任何重大困擾或痛苦。<ref name="hawkinson">{{cite journal | author = Hawkinson, K., & Zamboni, B. D. | year = 2014 | title = Adult Baby/Diaper Lovers: An Exploratory Study of an Online Community Sample | journal = Archives of Sexual Behavior | volume = 43 | issue = 5 | pages = 863–877 | doi=10.1007/s10508-013-0241-7}}</ref>

